From 8487f93db8550af32c9b612ee83008100ca5cf67 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Arnaldo Carvalho de Melo <acme@redhat.com>
Date: Thu, 2 Jan 2025 16:50:39 -0300
Subject: [PATCH 173/388] perf top: Don't complain about lack of vmlinux when
