Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20241230-topic-misc-dt-fixes-v4-4-1e6880e9dda3@linaro.org
Signed-off-by: Bjorn Andersson <andersson@kernel.org>
Signed-off-by: Sasha Levin <sashal@kernel.org>
